**  ERROR
E-01 UPDATE INSTRUCTION <0 1 2>
E-02 INPUT SHIPPING#
E-03 NO DATA
E-04 DATA IS CANCELLED ALREADY
E-05 NO DATA
E-06 DATA EXIST
E-07 INPUT L.T.
E-08 CAN'T USE SYMBOLS -> #%&@/_\+-|?!
E-09
E-10
E-11 INPUT TIME
E-12 RANGE IS 00:00 -- 23:59  OR  99:99
E-13 INPUT DATE
E-14 DATE ERROR
E-15
E-16
E-17
E-18
E-19
E-20
**  ERROR SYMBOL
#\%&@/_$+-|?!
